            </a>
            <a href="https://outlook.office365.com/mail/" target="_blank" class="icon-card">
                <i>📧</i> <span>E-mail</span> <small>Outlook</small>
            </a>
            <a href="https://cc.claro.com.br/" target="_blank" class="icon-card">
                <i>🎧</i> <span>Nice</span> <small>Central Claro</small>
            </a>
        </div>
